com.vector.cfg.automation.scripting.base

Interface IScriptTaskExecutionResult


  • @PublishedApi(value=ADDITIONS_ALLOWED)
 @PublishedApiDomain(value=AUTOMATION_IF)
 @Immutable
public interface IScriptTaskExecutionResult
    IScriptTaskExecutionResult represents the result of one IScriptTask execution. The result contains:
    • Return value of the task code
    • System out
    • System error
    • Logger entries made to the script logger, see IScript.getScriptLogger()

    All method parameters and return values must be non-null unless documented otherwise.
